						<p ALIGN="LEFT" class="subtitle">Chairmaking Tools
						<font size="2">
						<span style="font-weight: 400">by Christopher 
				Schwarz<br>
						</span></font>
						<font style="font-size: 8pt; font-weight: 400">Copyright 
